name: Pupshot
tag_list: dog, doggie, pup, puppy, photo, pic, sharing, community, network, social
overview: Pupshot is an exciting new way to share your dog with family, friends, and the world, 1,000 words at a time. Join the Pupshot community of dog lovers and strike up conversations while comparing your favorite photos. Follow your favorite dogs to create a personal photo stream or browse through the newest photos. Pupshot is not just another social network, our website is a fun community for dog lovers to share their best friends.
